column5: Lets hear about your Big Walleye this year.Where, When, On What? Lac Seul/June14/30"/Jig Minnow
28 1/8 June 21, Lac Seul, 4:30 pm 27 1/2" June 21, Lac Seul 5:15 pm Good Day:rockit:
Yoke Lake 28" & 29" back to back Lindy rig and leech 7/6/07
LOTW 7/22/2007 30" on a jig and Leech

Proud to announce 4 10 lb eyes this June on Georgian Bay, one for me, one each for my 2 sons, and one for my father in law. Truly a dream trip: One on a live bait rig One on a 1/4 oz jig and worm One on a twister tail jig and worm One on a 1/2 oz Vib-E blade bait. And we lost another 10 and approx 8 lb eye at the boat....
June 17, 2007 Central Lac Seul 30.5" Jig and minnow Biggest walleye of my life (so far) Cheers....IA Walleye
